Summary: 
 * Added FacadeTraits<const T>
 - where FacadeTraits<const T>::Ref == FacadeTraits<T>::ConstRef
 - and   FacadeTraits<const T>::Ptr == FacadeTraits<T>::ConstPtr, i.e.,
 - If the facade object is const we can only get pointers to const
   objects even if we request a normal pointer.
